The Practice Is Level 0
The practice of recognition is independent of which branch is correct. This is the most important practical consequence of the meta-structure.

1. Notice any arising — thought, sensation, perception, emotion.
2. Observe the implicit claim: "I am the one experiencing this."  [Sv(0)]
3. Look completely at who the "I" is.
4. Watch the claim dissolve.  [¬Sv(0)]

This procedure operates at L0.4–5. It does not require committing to Branch 4 (consciousness as substrate). It does not require belief in karma, Platonic forms, or physical reductionism. The Sv(0) error is a structural feature of any observer embedded in S. Its cessation is available regardless of what S ultimately is.
This is why the Zen koan, the Madhyamaka dialectic, the Advaita self-inquiry, and the Christian via negativa all arrive at structurally similar phenomenological reports despite incompatible metaphysics. They are all operating at Level 0.


Document Architecture
The complete Tractatus Conscientiae now has the following layered structure:

Level 0  —  This document (Addendum)
         6 propositions. Ontologically neutral.
         Formally necessary. The condition of any interpretation.


Level 1  —  Interpretation Branches (B1–B6)
         Each specifies what occupies S.
         Branch 4 = Nondual Metaphysics = main Tractatus.


Level 2  —  Tractatus Conscientiae v0.1 (main document)
         Axioms A1–A7 are now theorems within Branch 4.
         Propositions 1–9 follow within Branch 4.


Level 3  —  Mechanism candidates (M-nodes)
         Multiple per proposition. Empirically distinguishable.


Level 4  —  Evidence nodes (EN-nodes)
         Open / partial / confirmed / falsified.


Level 5  —  AI tracking layer
         Probability weights. Literature scanning.
         Evidence-to-node mapping. Version control.

The spine is stable from Level 0 to Level 2. The mechanism candidates and evidence nodes change continuously. Level 0 changes only if something can appear without any enabling condition, observer, or observed — i.e., if appearance itself is possible without the three-term structure. No such case has been identified.



The structure is empty. The pointer points. Recognition dissolves even this.
